title: Microsoft Office Professional Plus 2019 Build 10820 x64
description:
Microsoft Office Professional Plus 2019 Version 1809 (Build 16.0.10820.20006)

Optional: Microsoft Project Professional 2019 Version 1809 (Build 16.0.10820.20006) and Microsoft Visio Professional 2019 Version 1809 (Build 16.0.10820.20006)

Language: German (Germany), English (United States), Spanish (Spain), French (France), Italian (Italy), Polish (Poland), Portuguese (Brazil), and Swedish (Sweden)

Channel: Insider 

Credits: Click-to-Run (C2R) installation provided by Ratiborus

To prepare:

1. Uninstall Microsoft Office 2016 (or any MSO version installed).
2. Windows 10 Installed (Windows 8.1/8/7/Vista are not supported)
	
How to Install:
1. On the Main tab of the installer, select "Microsoft Office 2019"
2. Select x86 or x64
3. Confirm office version and single products
4. Click install office
	   
How to Update: In the application menu, go to "File>Account>Office Updates"

Due to resource limitations, please help me seed these distributions
